                    <span>MOB!!! Crazy!!! Off the hook!!! Didn't want to put it down!! Roy did his thing with MOB. Great characters, great storyline, great intensity! I can't wait until Drug Related comes out so I can see what happened to Travis and the crew. MOB is a definite must read!!
