                    <span>Roy Glenn has crafted an excellent tale of suspense and street drama interwoven with a love story.
<br />Will love conquer all or will the motto of the crew ( Money over Bi***es) be the law of the day ?  You must read MOB to find out. 
<br />
<br />If you read Mr. Glenn's previous novel , Is It A Crime, you can see his growth as a writer. I am anxiously awaiting his next release in April. </span>
                  
              
